\item Jiang, Z., et al. (2016). The determinants and impacts of aesthetics in users' first interaction with websites. \textit{Journal of Management Information Systems}, 33(1), 229-259.
\item Kim, J., Hahn, J., \& Hahn, H. (2000). How do we understand a system with (so) many diagrams? Cognitive integration processes in diagrammatic reasoning. \textit{Information Systems Research}, 11(3), 284-303.
