\item Sim, J., et al. (2024). In-consumption information cues and online video consumption. \textit{MIS Quarterly}, 48(2), 645-678.
\item Speier, C., \& Morris, M. G. (2003). The influence of query interface design on decision-making performance. \textit{MIS Quarterly}, 27(3), 397-423.
\item Vance, A., et al. (2025). The Fog of Warnings: How Non-Security-Related Notifications Diminish the Efficacy of Security Warnings. \textit{MIS Quarterly}, 49(4), 1357-1384.
